data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Nestled on a beautiful, wooded lot, this elegant smart home built by Meritage in 2017 stands proudly in the sought-after community of COUNTRY WALK, a subdivision of Meadow Point in Wesley Chapel. From the moment you arrive, the picturesque scene unfolds before you: a home with energy-efficient features, a meticulously maintained emerald-green lawn, freshly mulched landscaping, and charming exterior accents such as vibrant shutters framing the front windows, coach lights flank the garage doors, and a welcoming portico entrance. Spanning 2,499 sf this residence offers a thoughtfully designed living space with 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, and a 2-car garage, with an open concept split bedroom floor plan. As you step inside you will be greeted by large format tile floors that seamlessly flow throughout the living area. The kitchen, a haven for culinary enthusiasts, boasts richly appointed 42-inch antique-white cabinets adorned with crown molding. A subway-style tile backsplash complements the smooth top range, and stainless appliances include a double wall oven, microwave, dishwasher and French Door refrigerator. A granite counter-height island extends gracefully and creates a gathering place for guests to sit and interact with the chef and is illuminated by pendant lighting. Adjacent to the kitchen, the breakfast room features sliding glass doors overlooking the lanai. The kitchen connects to the expansive family room creating endless possibilities for entertainment. Additionally, there is an office space with cabinets, a granite-topped desk and filing drawers, making it the perfect spot for homework, a computer room or cozy reading area. The master retreat features a tray ceiling, and a contrasting color accent wall with triple windows that fill the space with natural light. Laminate floors add a touch of sophistication, and the ensuite bath provides a retreat. Indulge in the deep soaking tub surrounded by tile, or step into the spacious tiled shower with a bench seat. Separate vanities with undermount sinks offer ample counter space and are topped with granite. The master suite also offers two large walk-in closets and convenient access to the laundry room. Bedrooms 3 and 4 are generously sized and feature laminate flooring. An expansive screen enclosed lanai is an idyllic setting for social gatherings and is set against a backdrop of lush green lawn and wooded area behind the home. Country Walk offers an array of amenities including a clubhouse, fitness center, basketball and tennis courts, soccer field, covered playground, and dog park. Acres of natural open space surround the community. This prime location grants easy access to Tampa’s finest activities, shopping, dining, and entertainment. Embrace the Florida lifestyle and make this remarkable home your own! Call today to schedule your personal tour!
